        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>BackDate – where dating becomes simpler 🖤👅</h1>
            <p>With BackDate, you save the time spent on endless swiping and chatting. You give us your schedule, and we arrange the dates for you. 😉🖤</p>
            <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn">Learn more 💀</a>
