            <ol>
                <li><strong>Calendar. 🗓️</strong> Choose your available days for meetings.</li>
                <li><strong>Profile. 📝</strong> Share your interests and preferences.</li>
                <li><strong>Sync. 🔄</strong> Connect your favorite dating apps.</li>
                <li><strong>Magic. ✨🖤</strong> We’ll arrange the best dates for you!</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </section>

