                    <img src="assets/icon2.svg" alt="Personalization">
                    <h3>Personalization 🖤🎯</h3>
                    <p>We consider your interests and preferences. 💌</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <img src="assets/icon3.svg" alt="Privacy">
